From: Wally Gleemer <Wally.Gleemer@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 25 Mar 2008 16:21:33 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] cavium: Add executive to include path

Ensure cvmx.h and friends are found by putting them explicicly into
the include path.

Signed-off-by: Wally Gleemer <Wally.Gleemer@windriver.com>
---
 arch/mips/cavium-octeon/Makefile |    4 ++++
 1 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/mips/cavium-octeon/Makefile b/arch/mips/cavium-octeon/Makefile
index 0d5e8b9..5fdf0e9 100644
--- a/arch/mips/cavium-octeon/Makefile
+++ b/arch/mips/cavium-octeon/Makefile
@@ -9,6 +9,10 @@
 # Copyright (C) 2005-2007 Cavium Networks
 #
 
+OCTEON_ROOT = $(srctree)/arch/mips/cavium-octeon
+EXTRA_CFLAGS +=	-I$(OCTEON_ROOT)/gpl-executive/config \
+		-I$(OCTEON_ROOT)/executive
+
 obj-y := setup.o serial.o irq.o hal.o perf_counters.o octeon_info.o
 obj-y += dma-octeon.o userio.o flash_setup.o
 obj-y += pci_console.o
